  "name": "Neverland",
  "description": "Neverland is a Monad-native non-custodial lending protocol built on the Aave V3 framework, reimagining DeFi incentives through self-repaying loans, flexible NFT-based veToken governance, and automation. It redistributes 100% of protocol revenue back to the community through governance-directed rewards, liquidity incentives, and deflationary buybacks and burns.",
